            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:334dce8e-3bd3-408d-9a48-a3b700a0101d</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/workplace_safety/~3/euhMnL_gC9k/how-safe-workplace</link>
