            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:0740f435-e8ab-4846-b24b-a1c000a7d200</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/workplace_safety/~3/sxi5aRa5syY/manufacturer-safety-violations</link>
