            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:722532ac-0e96-4277-949f-9e700086eddd</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/workplace_safety/~3/vvN4yj0TXm8/Prohibit-employees-cell-phones</link>
